@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sxvlhq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.abs(v1))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.sin(v0))
    v2 = (0.13 / (wp.sin(v2 + 0.65) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.40)))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v2 + 0.68) * (v0 + 0.56 / v1 + 0.83)) + (wp.abs(tmp + 0.37) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.33)))
    data[tid] = v0
